<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83b700c1bd20caec57a7d359e2a9d763d6f25df","tid":21320,"uid":1585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T16:00:43.000Z","msg":"新濠high tea"},{"pid":"7ed8bba4debf29829032a2d186606e8bfab3c2a8","tid":21320,"uid":34785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:05:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真 澳門d野好柒貴同難食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解我覺得平過同好食過香港，好多街坊鋪頭出品都好有水準"},{"pid":"4b2d84cd3281b60040fc5413cb8cb07e6b8c94b4","tid":21320,"uid":23872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:17:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我都唔明點解咁多香港人鐘意去澳門<br />\n你話要去賭錢叫雞既話，我就冇野好講<br />\n其他既話我諗唔到咩係香港冇澳門有<br />\n睇下香港啲商場，再去睇下澳門果啲<br />\n跟本冇得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落後地方，地方又細，仲要四周圍都係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 情況絕對嚴重過香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"1ed08209ea741a5aacef5a95d121157390b08360","tid":21320,"uid":23872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:19:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真 澳門d野好柒貴同難食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解我覺得平過同好食過香港，好多街坊鋪頭出品都好有水準</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">平？邊撚到平<br />\n我完全唔覺<br />\n香港啲餐廳好過澳門果啲九條街</span><br />\n<br />\n澳門人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4f709ff028b1272686851da87031b30fd20c41","tid":21320,"uid":21262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:26:01.000Z","msg":"安德魯葡撻出名但冇想像中好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大三巴廣場有間黃枝記 印象中好似咁既名 食雲吞麵 幾好味"},{"pid":"43efbb53aa67068b2c10a03242b771090ee46009","tid":21320,"uid":8042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12